parameters: \n<Ruin>...What are you talking about? And who are you, anyway?
\n<Gargan>Who I am? Such things are irrelevant to you.
ルイン立ち絵 驚き
\n<Gargan>Ruin. I have thoroughly investigated everything about you.

\n<Gargan>Your technology extracts energy from living beings and
creates machines that behave as if they have a will of their
own.

\n<Gargan>It has been deemed dangerous and has never been recognized
by anyone.

\n<Gargan>A deal to lead your sworn enemies, the modified girls, to
ruin.
\n<Ruin>Indeed, I hate Marion. But that's just one-sided resentment.
\n<Ruin>I can't agree to such a deal.

\n<Gargan>The poison of a demon that is corroding your mother's body.
I shall teach you the method to cure it.
ルイン立ち絵 驚き

\n<Gargan>However, it will be a success fee. You will have to act as I
instruct you.

\n<Gargan>The condition is that the monsters you create must defeat
the modified girls.
